{"tid":1719533,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【國際戰線】港警於韓國KBS節目承認強姦，點解冇人講","createTime":"2019-11-14T06:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T05:21:36.000Z","uid":280046,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"aff33156bb5bc1e45dea208bb2803c88883a3108","tid":1719533,"uid":280046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:13:59.000Z","msg":"KBS係韓國大電視台，有一定公信力，相信佢地有fc，但而家twitter好似冇人講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zz1ar0r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZz1ar0r.jpg&h=0c078f75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5SAuHyM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5SAuHyM.jpg&h=89cd2576&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e85347a463e0dcdefb35c1bd237a4ef0d8a27af","tid":1719533,"uid":250951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:15:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"05cd617ee2a16eac8ae731e4bc7c02ab72a075c3","tid":1719533,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:16:04.000Z","msg":"講左幾日 有上熱門<br />\ntwitter都有人推到"},{"pid":"b19c4c5621b9fb39b5d0c3be6872661111d7fbe4","tid":1719533,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T12:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2c4935eddb9bd25ac93c33960f1661588f7cb6","tid":1719533,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T12:37:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尋找黑警性暴力證人/受害者，協助國際遊說</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2640629789347426%26id%3D124616407615456&d=7CNMK8%2FfTiCK2iXV1c%2BwrByAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=bb153d22\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\nPost：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eDEkrT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eDEkrT</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"8216c5404cf5379ee6f231643092bf6a41f73bfd","tid":1719533,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05558f07d88abea1a6ba4fc747c80e0ca0b34cfe","tid":1719533,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T15:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f3bb15b2a804cc49f810b6cf88f9e442b6e3c8","tid":1719533,"uid":266755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05cd617ee2a16eac8ae731e4bc7c02ab72a075c3","tid":1719533,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:16:04.000Z","msg":"講左幾日 有上熱門<br />\ntwitter都有人推到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T15:13:10.000Z","msg":"yep, 我都twit過，所羅門都twit過"},{"pid":"e7b50d7201c700677b7b53ba0732786455100c69","tid":1719533,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T23:36:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed33aa5fedf74247cfd71a53e8b763f07f1ff7a","tid":1719533,"uid":87723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T23:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c21bf50ca8d170bc5804c46e0802d57fc57b85b","tid":1719533,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T00:02:03.000Z","msg